see their docstrings for the details:
   * `mu4e-read-option': read one option from a list. For example:
           (mu4e-read-option "Choose an animal: "
              '(("Monkey" . monkey) ("Gnu" . gnu) ("xMoose" . moose)))
     The user is presented with:
